WEBVTT

00:00:06.908 --> 00:00:08.800
Zamislite ovo:

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:10.432
u dubokom ste snu

00:00:10.432 --> 00:00:12.762
i odjednom se budite!

00:00:12.762 --> 00:00:14.480
Nije vas probudio alarm.

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:15.723
Oči su vam otvorene,

00:00:15.723 --> 00:00:17.788
a demon vam sedi na grudima

00:00:17.788 --> 00:00:19.373
i prikovani ste za krevet.

00:00:19.373 --> 00:00:21.343
Pokušavate da otvorite usta i vrištite,

00:00:21.343 --> 00:00:22.679
ali ne proizvodite zvuk.

00:00:22.679 --> 00:00:24.548
Pokušavate da ustanete i pobegnete,

00:00:24.548 --> 00:00:27.367
ali shvatate da ste potpuno nepokretni.

00:00:27.367 --> 00:00:29.561
Demon pokušava da vas uguši,

00:00:29.561 --> 00:00:31.520
ali ne možete da se odbranite.